        "messages": {
          "209980000": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980000,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "Hello, {NICKNAME}!",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980001
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980001": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980001,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "Great news! Just a few moments ago, Miss Kaimee's calculations showed that the memoria loss at Dreamflux Reef has stopped entirely.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980002
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980002": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980002,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "The work you've put into the Dreamscape is deeply appreciated. I can't thank you enough.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980003,
              209980004
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980003": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980003,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": null,
            "text": "That's fantastic news! I'm sure Dreamflux Reef will recover soon enough",
            "option": "That's fantastic news!",
            "nextIds": [
              209980005
            ],
            "kind": "Player"
          },
          "209980005": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980005,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "Gallagher and Mikhail would've wanted to express their appreciation too, but I guess now I must convey it on their behalf.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980006
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980006": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980006,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "I remember when you all first arrived in Penacony, Gallagher was so nervous and hopeful after hearing of it. It's not every day that he gets that way.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980007
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980007": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980007,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "Don't let his laid-back demeanor deceive you. Every time he spoke with you, he'd carefully think through his words beforehand.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980008
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980008": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980008,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "Mikhail was the same way. If he could see how outstanding the younger generation is, he'd be thrilled.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980009,
              209980011
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980009": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980009,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": null,
            "text": "I didn't expect to see that side of Mr. Gallagher!",
            "option": "Is that so...",
            "nextIds": [
              209980010
            ],
            "kind": "Player"
          },
          "209980010": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980010,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": null,
            "text": "If only they were still here...",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980013
            ],
            "kind": "PlayerAuto"
          },
          "209980013": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980013,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "But there's no need to feel so down about it.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980014
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980014": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980014,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "Mikhail's wish has been fulfilled, and Gallagher kept his promise after a long and seemingly endless wait.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980015
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980015": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980015,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "The dream shouldn't rest on the shoulders of one person when it's a vision we all share.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980016
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980016": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980016,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "From Mikhail's grandfather, to Mikhail, to Gallagher, and now to you guys...",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980017
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980017": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980017,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "They may have left us, but the dream of the Nameless continues to thrive. That's the greatest solace we can offer them.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980018
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980018": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980018,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "Eventually, you'll embark on a new journey. When you do, may you connect with more worlds and carry the dream of trailblazing across the Cosmos.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980019
            ],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980019": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980019,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": 154,
            "text": "Please take this token of our appreciation.",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [],
            "kind": "NPC"
          },
          "209980011": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980011,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": null,
            "text": "Their dream has come true, but they can no longer see it themselves...",
            "option": "That's truly unfortunate...",
            "nextIds": [
              209980012
            ],
            "kind": "Player"
          },
          "209980012": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980012,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": null,
            "text": "That's truly unfortunate...",
            "option": null,
            "nextIds": [
              209980013
            ],
            "kind": "PlayerAuto"
          },
          "209980004": {
            "type": "Text",
            "id": 209980004,
            "sectionId": 2099800,
            "senderId": null,
            "text": "All in a day's work for the Nameless",
            "option": "It was nothing",
            "nextIds": [
              209980005
            ],
            "kind": "Player"
          }
        }
      }
    ]
